{"tid":724935,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解間間U都有Graduate Employment Survey, 但恒大冇既?","createTime":"2018-07-01T10:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T10:38:37.000Z","uid":133727,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d20d9cac0df15445f38260553d7355cd7d6eb65c","tid":724935,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"搵左成日, 得哩份有提過下Graduate Employment:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hsmc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/HSMC-Review-2016-2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsmc.edu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FHSMC-Review-2016-2017.pdf&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=acf6ee32\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hsmc.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/HSMC-Review-2016-2017.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\np.8<br />\nGraduate Employment and Student Internship An annual employment survey focusing on fresh graduates was conducted by the Student Affairs Office (SAO) during the period from October 2016 to February 2017 on their employment status, remuneration and job-seeking experience. <span style=\"color: red;\">The response rate was 90%</span>, representing a reply from 1,283 bachelor&rsquo;s degree graduates. <br />\n<br />\n(好叻喎恒大, 有90% response rate <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The overall engagement rate of graduates in employment or further studies was close to 92%</span>. According to an independent survey commissioned by SAO in 2015-16, employers regard our graduates as <span style=\"color: red;\">having good working attitudes and interpersonal skills, receptible to new ideas and opinions from others, devoted, responsible and always willing to take up further responsibilities.</span> In general, HSMC graduates have made positive impressions on their employers who often express appreciation and willingness to hire our students and graduates. <br />\n<br />\n(哦哦哦, 知喇知喇, 恒大仔好高評價嘛, 數據呢? 得啲terms, 中學生作文呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n)<br />\n<br />\n恒大打飛機真係叻, 打咁多字黎自我滿足<br />\n但點解畢業生平均收入唔講, 份independent survey又唔出report既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地東大都有肯講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twc.edu.hk/uploads/publications/pdf/TWC-Annual-Report_2015-2016.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twc.edu.hk%2Fuploads%2Fpublications%2Fpdf%2FTWC-Annual-Report_2015-2016.pdf&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=b5590b95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twc.edu.hk/uploads/publications/pdf/TWC-Annual-Report_2015-2016.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nP.45<br />\nAverage Monthly Salary of Full-time Employed Graduates<br />\n全職就業畢業生平均月薪<br />\nBachelor&rsquo;s degree graduates<br />\n學士畢業生 $20,552 <br />\n<br />\nHKU:<a href=\"http://cedars.hku.hk/sections/careersplacement/GraduateEmploymentSurvey/report/FD/FD_report_2015.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcedars.hku.hk%2Fsections%2Fcareersplacement%2FGraduateEmploymentSurvey%2Freport%2FFD%2FFD_report_2015.pdf&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=66ec9b1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://cedars.hku.hk/sections/careersplacement/GraduateEmploymentSurvey/report/FD/FD_report_2015.pdf</a><br />\nCU:<a href=\"http://www.osa.cuhk.edu.hk/publication-statistics/graduate-employment-survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.osa.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fpublication-statistics%2Fgraduate-employment-survey&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=a2f7a17b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.osa.cuhk.edu.hk/publication-statistics/graduate-employment-survey</a><br />\nUST:<a href=\"https://career.ust.hk/web/public/documents/StatisticalSummary_UG_2016.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcareer.ust.hk%2Fweb%2Fpublic%2Fdocuments%2FStatisticalSummary_UG_2016.pdf&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=d0b0ee61\" target=\"_blank\">https://career.ust.hk/web/public/documents/StatisticalSummary_UG_2016.pdf</a><br />\nPoly: <a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/caps/es/images/web_doc/Poly_Graduate_Employment_Survey_2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fcaps%2Fes%2Fimages%2Fweb_doc%2FPoly_Graduate_Employment_Survey_2017.pdf&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=129f7026\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/caps/es/images/web_doc/Poly_Graduate_Employment_Survey_2017.pdf</a><br />\nBU:<a href=\"https://sa.hkbu.edu.hk/career/f/page/973/11386/ges2016.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsa.hkbu.edu.hk%2Fcareer%2Ff%2Fpage%2F973%2F11386%2Fges2016.pdf&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=8e066d3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://sa.hkbu.edu.hk/career/f/page/973/11386/ges2016.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n全部都大大方方, 係你恒大: In general, HSMC graduates have made positive impressions on their employers who often express appreciation and willingness to hire our students and graduates. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e094359a0333a6d78d07a27647e57d729b51c10","tid":724935,"uid":184726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"因為佢唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">U</span>囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244b2b58ab7b05092671a5d994229b9477c99d14","tid":724935,"uid":133